00:20:58.929 --> 00:21:08.700
the world who can't live the life that their
mom or dad lived, right? Who are asking themselves

00:21:08.700 --> 00:21:13.190
all sorts of "who am I" questions and are
now asking not only what does it mean to be

00:21:13.190 --> 00:21:20.039
a Pentecostal in Brazil or a Catholic in Nebraska
