00:21:27.399 --> 00:21:34.899
Pentecostals, Israeli Jews, Indian Hindus,
American Catholics, right? Who am I in this

00:21:34.899 --> 00:21:41.040
world? How do I relate to those people? There
is an enormous energy at the intersection

00:21:41.040 --> 00:21:46.369
of those four trends and the thing that scares
me is the people who figured that energy out

00:21:46.369 --> 00:21:50.039
first are religious extremist movements, ok?

00:21:50.039 --> 00:21:55.980
I view extremist movements from Al-Qaeda to
the Christian Identity Movement to their equivalents

00:21:55.980 --> 00:22:02.470
in every faith and they have equivalents in
