00:22:38.409 --> 00:22:43.920
to do is dominate those other people, right?"

00:22:43.920 --> 00:22:52.259
These religious extremist movements recruit,
train, network, and mobilize young people

00:22:52.259 --> 00:22:58.220
to be the foot soldiers of religious extremism.
