00:23:32.539 --> 00:23:37.529
who believes in a world of pluralism, who
believes in a world where people from different

00:23:37.529 --> 00:23:41.450
backgrounds live in equal dignity and mutual
loyalty.

00:23:41.450 --> 00:23:45.980
A world where people's identities are respected,
